metadata.name: 7 Pepes & Claude
metadata.description:
Claude took a trip down to Pepe's Pond in search of a few plants to bring back to the GreenHouse. He got distracted and picked up a magical Pepe which sent him into a deep trance. 

Find all 7 Pepes to help Claude snap out of his trance

Bonus: Find 5 flies to feed to the Pepes and the 3 house plants to bring back to the GreenHouse
